Text: Through it all, there will be something special for the original devotees who joined us on this adventure. And, when the time comes, Vault will be fully revealed, unlocking a new world of wonders to all those who believe. Stay tuned.

At the center of past, present, and future, Vault will forever reflect upon Gucci’s centennial history and its future legacy. With our experimental ethos, we will invite creatives to turn dreams into reality as they sculpt the story of the next hundred years.
Letting ingenuity lead the way, something exquisite might emerge as Vault calls upon a certain digital artisan to reimagine the historic knowhow of Gucci.

Future—The Next Hundred Years
We are thrilled and honored to embark on this imaginative journey with you, the Discord community of Vault. Together, we will travel across dimensions through uncharted digital realms in search of deeper connections.

Inspired by a profound desire to explore new playgrounds, Vault recently chose to acquire parcels of land in The Sandbox metaverse. Voxel by voxel, our bespoke world will become an eclectic space fostering boundary-pushing creativity.

The 500 digital pieces that arose from this collection continue to garner mainstream attention in anticipation of the upcoming distribution of ceramic sculptures, handcrafted in Italy, which are to be delivered to the owners of the corresponding SUPERGUCCI NFTs.

Vault aims to embrace Web3 by delving deep into the metaverse through the creation of nonfungible tokens (NFTs). By lining our shelves with physical and digital assets from different eras, ideas hybridize and create those perfect conditions to spark new creativity for the future.
The name elicits an aura of magic and represents a free-dimensional place where past, present, and future can coexist through the power of the imagination.

Beginnings- The Opening of Vault:
Vault is an experimental concept space created by Gucci from the vision of Creative Director Alessandro Michele.

Discover Vault’s Way:
Worlds within worlds, 
rooms within rooms, 
like nothing you’ve ever seen, 
yet like everything you’ve ever known. 
This is Vault. 
Where it will take us? 
That’s a surprise by design, 
but hopefully this roadmap 
will let you surmise.
